{"tid":292416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上聯署反對蔡若蓮任教育副局長　楊潤雄：不評人選、用人唯才","createTime":"2017-06-21T11:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T13:10:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edd836a365101759224b328a17098e3a41983bbb","tid":292416,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:13:14.000Z","msg":"《星島日報》今日報道指，教育局副局長將由教育工作者聯會（教聯會）副主席蔡若蓮出任，隨即惹來教育界猛烈批評。繼立法會教育界議員葉建源以及教協發聲反對，網上有人教育界人士發起聯署，反對蔡若蓮擔任教育局副局長。截至四時半，聯署一共取得大約350個簽名。候任教育局長楊潤雄今日稱，副局長聘任工作仍在進行中，不會評論人選，但考慮副局長人選會以用人唯才為原則。<br />\n<br />\n聯署表示，對有關傳聞「極感驚訝」和「強烈反對」，指出蔡若蓮來自的教聯會是「一個傳統親共的『愛國組織』」，曾推出洗腦國民教育教材，舉辦大量廉價愛國交流團等，她的背景必令公眾對政府未來的教育政策完全失去信心，「絕對不能接受」。<br />\n<br />\n聯署亦提到，蔡若蓮在2016年的立法會教育界選舉中落敗，得票不足三成，「可見她的能力、她的政治取向，得不到教育界的大多數支持」。發起人質問政府委任落敗者成為問責官員，「是否準備與教育界為敵？」，亦形容此舉是「對選民的公然侮辱」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%A5%E8%93%AE%E4%BB%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%89%AF%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&d=ISdeuin%2BCt4GA%2BY9SdWPfvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=8f1e4c8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2593%25AE%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&h=41bd3361\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%A5%E8%93%AE%E4%BB%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%89%AF%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7/</a>"},{"pid":"da3e32fa786b676882d2887bb2a0917676431713","tid":292416,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"又一個洗腦集團"},{"pid":"a79e9a15dfa9d1e605e6d864ef97729cba13e5c1","tid":292416,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"6e0df57c9cd684b731bb773b0df1dfb64d244eef","tid":292416,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:16:48.000Z","msg":"根本香港人宜加乜柒都無得say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77eb07cd5a831cfba9b7635cb8302080847759c","tid":292416,"uid":122718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51c485548519af01420c5721da47ec1235437577","tid":292416,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:10:03.000Z","msg":"唔垃圾又點做到呢個位呢？"}]}